metadata.name: 【Jun.】Moonstone
metadata.description:
Moonstone meaning : Health, Good fortune, Fertility,Premonition of love

Moonstone is characterized by a mysterious moonlight-like light called "Schiller," which in ancient times was said to be the solidification of moonlight. It is said to have been worn as a talisman, with folklore that it enhanced healing power and precognition in many parts of the world.
In Japan, the moon's pattern is seen as a rabbit pounding rice cakes, and the rabbit is an animal traditionally associated with the moon.
